                    <p>"Kloof Schools Launch Innovative School Feeding Scheme to Ensure Every Child Thrives"</p>
                    <p class="date">26/06/2023</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Read more</a>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="news-item">
                <img src="~/Images/comdev.png" alt="Community Development">
                <div class="news-content">
                    <h2>Community Development</h2>
                    <p>"Empowering Rural Communities: New Initiatives Drive Sustainable Development in Remote Areas"</p>
                    <p class="date">24/06/2023</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Read more</a>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="news-item">
                <img src="~/Images/food.png" alt="Food Drives">
                <div class="news-content">
                    <h2>Food Drives</h2>
                    <p>"Community Unites: Food Drive Brings Hope to Underdeveloped Suburbs in KZN"</p>
                    <p class="date">18/06/2023</p>
                    <a href="#" class="read-more">Read more</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </section>
        <button class="view-more">View more</button>
        <section class="gallery">
